title: 2021 CFB Pick Em Week 14
description:
El Pres, Big Cat & Rico Bosco are back for the last episode of the year before the bowl special. Dave is riding high off Michigan's win and Rico lost 10.5 units on Ohio State. Will anyone win the Pat Hill trophy?


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/barstoolpickem
